latestIgtvVideos.caption:
15.01.1965 
I have that tattooed on my hand because that was the day the world’s most beautiful human being was born, you my mother are the most beautiful from the inside and outside. 
Thank you so much for just being yourself, being the best mother on the face of this planet, like Bhaiya says, we love showing you off because we know you’re the best anyone can have. 
You’re my best friend and honestly I take pride when I say that because the relationship I share w you, I haven’t seen that anywhere. You make it so easy to find a friend in a mother, that’s rare. You’re the strongest woman I know, the way you live your life is a joy to look at, you should write a book seriously. 
Your guidance, morals, principles and values are the reason I am who I am today & I’m pretty fucking great ;) You’ve moulded me in the best possible way, you’ve held my hand through the darkest times. You were there for me when I needed a best friend the most and for that I will thank you everyday. You got me out of the drain and watered me everyday and saw me bloom. Thankyou so much for everything and more.
Making this video was hard because now I miss you so much. You’ve given me everything I have today, you’re the reason I am me and I can’t wait to come squish you and love you and of course, burp on you & maybe smell some farts. I LOVE U!! Happy birthday to the world’s best mother, my best friend, Simi Sabhaney 💕
@simi.sabhaney
